  "title": "Containerizing Microservices with FastAPI in Python 3.12+",
  "summary": "This explainer demonstrates how to containerize microservices using FastAPI, a modern, fast (high-performance), web framework for building APIs with Python 3.12+. Docker is utilized for containerization.",

